snippet.title: The Land of the Magnates - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Watch the release date announcement trailer for The Land of the Magnates, an action-adventure puzzle RPG developed by Permanent Way Games. Players will embark on an epic adventure rooted in Middle Eastern myths and legends as a disgraced prince. Defeat enemies along the path, travel to magical realms, and reclaim the throne. The Land of the Magnates is launching on August 27 for PC (Steam).
